sources.title: Harlequin: The Awakening - Full Movie
sources.description:
Quiet, unassuming Sara McAllister uncovers a wonderful new woman that she never knew existed — herself. Flynn, a bounty hunter who’s tracking one of her tenants, convinces her to join him in an adventure that takes them into the dangerous world of international espionage and love.
